OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Best of
OL,8,Fthe sunshine in the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,11,Fsome late brightness. Then outbreaks
OL,12,Fof rain will spread northeast for a
OL,13,Ftime overnight before it turns drier
OL,14,Flater.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,17,Fsunny spells along with scattered slow
OL,18,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy in
OL,19,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
