OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Wednesday but rain spreading
OL,7,Feast later. A few early showers on
OL,8,FThursday, otherwise dry, bright and
OL,9,Fbreezy. Rain spreading east on Friday.
